PrecisOrder exempting HARBOURFRONT CORPORATION and each of its wholly-owned subsidiaries from the requirement to conduct an internal audit of its operations for a three year period beginning in the 1991/92 fiscal year, on the grounds that the benefits derived from such audits do not justify their cost.
